# Desktop capture frames (use npm run pr:attach-captures to embed via Gist in PR body)
docs/pr-assets/tauri-desktop/*.png
docs/pr-assets/tauri-desktop/*.mp4
!docs/pr-assets/tauri-desktop/.gitkeep
